17:39.170 --> 17:40.840
- What's that supposed to mean?

17:40.840 --> 17:43.070
- All I know is my old man
said it just before

17:43.080 --> 17:46.010
he smacked the smile
off my face.

17:46.010 --> 17:48.710
- Peter.
- What is it?

17:48.710 --> 17:52.480
