18:29.050 --> 18:33.160
It's for the day officer jonesy
found the knife in question.

18:33.160 --> 18:34.860
- Any objections, Mr. stone?

18:34.860 --> 18:37.460
- Uh, none for the purpose
of this hearing.

18:37.460 --> 18:39.530
- The department
tracks its trucks.

18:39.530 --> 18:41.830
It knows exactly
where every truck is

18:41.830 --> 18:44.500
at every minute of the day.

18:44.500 --> 18:47.870
Please look at the column
for truck number four.

18:47.870 --> 18:52.480
When was it on the corner
of Radcliffe and main?

18:52.480 --> 18:54.110
7:17 A.M.

18:54.110 --> 18:58.220
- Picked up at 7:17.
