that waist-high trash

19:01.820 --> 19:05.520
where you found the knife
in that very dumpster.

19:05.520 --> 19:07.260
Now, who's lying,
officer jonesy?

19:07.260 --> 19:10.760
You or the computer
at the department of sanitation?

19:10.760 --> 19:12.060
