19:32.150 --> 19:35.290
2:00 A.M. until 9:21 A.M.

19:35.290 --> 19:37.920
That's almost 7 1/2 hours.

19:37.920 --> 19:39.920
Plenty of time to corrupt
the evidence.

19:39.930 --> 19:41.260
- Objection.
- Sustained.

19:41.260 --> 19:43.590
- Are you aware that by
knowingly signing

19:43.600 --> 19:46.530
