20:16.330 --> 20:19.260
- Was it in an evidence bag?
- Yes.

20:22.630 --> 20:26.100
- Was the car in your garage?

20:29.940 --> 20:32.810
- It was parked on the street
in front of my ex-wife's place.

20:32.810 --> 20:34.340
I slept there on the couch.
It was supposed to be

20:34.350 --> 20:37.610
my night with my kid,
but i... because I was working,

20:37.620 --> 20:41.820
and I just wanted to see him
before he went to school.

20:41.820 --> 20:46.360
But I did find the knife
in that dumpster.

20:46.360 --> 20:48.220
- No further questions.

20:48.230 --> 20:51.330
- In light of the witness's
admitted perjury

20:51.330 --> 20:55.000
