21:37.080 --> 21:39.910
- Hope there are
no hard feelings.

21:39.910 --> 21:42.050
You know what, stone?
You may not see it this way now,

21:42.050 --> 21:43.280
because you're fresh off
the fire,

21:43.280 --> 21:46.280
