I mean, the deck is kinda
stacked, isn't it?

21:56.030 --> 22:00.130
That's almost 13 million people
against one butcher.

22:00.130 --> 22:04.200
- Who killed two of them.

22:04.200 --> 22:05.970
- Whatever happened to bygones?

22:05.970 --> 22:08.740
- They don't exist for me.
It's my special problem.

22:08.740 --> 22:11.240
- Well, I recommend tums
for the agita.

22:11.240 --> 22:14.310
- It's more like
a Thorn in my paw.

22:14.310 --> 22:17.250
The further I walk, the deeper
