22:20.450 --> 22:22.450
- You wanna know what I think?

22:22.450 --> 22:24.750
I think this is it for you.

22:24.760 --> 22:28.390
Trying to put the bad guys away
day after day.

22:28.390 --> 22:30.430
The thing is, one morning,
you're gonna wake up,

22:30.430 --> 22:33.200
shave, brush your teeth,
look at yourself in the mirror

22:33.200 --> 22:38.970
and realize you're the one
in the cage.

22:38.970 --> 22:41.400
- But here I am.

22:50.950 --> 22:55.490
- Is there any chance
he didn't do it?

22:55.490 --> 22:57.020
- No.

22:57.020 --> 22:59.320
- What you know won't pay for
this cup of coffee.

22:59.320 --> 23:01.420
It's what you can prove
in court that counts.

23:01.430 --> 23:02.990
- And without the knife,
all I can prove

23:02.990 --> 23:05.900
is they had drinks together.

23:05.900 --> 23:08.060
- Why?

23:08.070 --> 23:11.170
- What?
- Why did Beckett kill Cody?

23:11.170 --> 23:13.900
- You know, technically, motive
