23:13.910 --> 23:16.340
- Well, it's part of
a good narrative.

23:16.340 --> 23:19.940
Did you ever think that Beckett
beat you on the arson case

23:19.950 --> 23:22.950
because he just told
a better story?

23:22.950 --> 23:24.850
- An insurance scam?
- No.

23:24.850 --> 23:30.190
A hard-working business man
being swallowed by debt.

23:30.190 --> 23:31.990
Juries can relate
to that, Peter.

23:31.990 --> 23:35.760
- So they ignore a murder?

23:35.760 --> 23:38.960
- Juries love a good story.

23:38.960 --> 23:40.500
Tell 'em one.

23:44.840 --> 23:46.200
- There's nothing
in Cody's email

23:46.200 --> 23:47.900
that suggests
he even knew Beckett.

23:47.910 --> 23:49.070
- We know they knew each other.

23:49.070 --> 23:50.440
- Well, they sure tried
to hide it.

23:50.440 --> 23:51.980
- Find out why.

23:51.980 --> 23:53.840
- There is something
