Ms. caufield.

28:02.060 --> 28:04.090
It's for how long.

28:04.100 --> 28:08.100
- A man was murdered.
You helped his killer go free.

28:08.100 --> 28:09.800
- People like you...
You'll never know.

28:09.800 --> 28:13.300
- The farmer, Paul Marcus...
